HEADWORD: Perfectly
<hw>Per"fect*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a perfect
manner or degree; in or to perfection; completely; wholly; thoroughly;
faultlessly.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Perfectly</xex> divine.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
